## Install instructions for the Adina toolbox ##

+ REQUIRED libraries
- spams ([1]), in particular the MATLAB version of the dictionary learning. Once compiled for your
  architecture, copy them in the SPAMS/.

+ Compilation
Before running the code, you MUST run "startup" script present in the
main directory. 

+ Datasets
Only reads sequence of image files that are able to read Matlab. The data MUST be motion compensated.

For any question or bug report, please feel free to contact me at:
ferran <dot> diego <at> iwr <dot> uni-heideleberg <dot> de

[1] http://spams-devel.gforge.inria.fr/

